node.text:
I want meow breakfast to be served at 6 AM. What part of MEOW do you not understand? 🙄

What time do you wake your hoomins up? 😂

__

Mập meow meow bao nhiêu lần rồi mà sen vẫn cứ không hiểu là sao? 🙄 5 giờ sáng thức dậy tán gẫu và chơi với Mập. 6 giờ sáng dọn mâm cho Mập ăn điểm tâm. Chỉ bấy nhiêu đó thôi mà cứ bắt Mập nhắc đi nhắc lại hoài à. 😤
__

No pawtato was harmed during bath time. 🥔 Human, however, suffered multiple lacerations, some contusions and at least one possible concussion. Just kidding! 😂🤣🙌🏻

Mama bear + pawpaw bear occasionally give Mochi a bath to help alleviate his skin allergies, feline acne and shedding with recommendations from our vet. 👩🏽‍⚕️🩺Mochi was a good boy and did very well, minus a little meowing at the beginning. 🥺

Mochi kindly asks online Karens to please open your minds and hearts before bullying and harassing Mochi’s little furmily with hurtful comments and DMs. 😿 Thank you for your understanding! 🙇🏻‍♂️🙇🏻‍♀️

Mochi is one busy chonky boi! 😹

—

The Secret Life of Mochi 🐻‍❄️🐾 

Often, human mistakenly thinks Mochi only eats sleeps plays repeats. However, little does human know Mochi lives a double cat life. 😜

Mochi assiduously spends hours watching CATFLIX to solve world hunger and tirelessly tapping Mochi’s happy paws to jazzercise just so Mochi can stay in a purrect round shape for human. 🥺🏐

So the next time human calls Mochi lazy … purrlease think again! 😭
